name: nw_framer_start_result_t
desc: Results that you send to indicate the disposition of your protocol after the start handler is invoked.

items.name: var nw_framer_start_result_ready: nw_framer_start_result_t
items.desc: The protocol is immediately ready to send and receive data.

items.name: var nw_framer_start_result_will_mark_ready: nw_framer_start_result_t
items.desc: The protocol will perform a handshake, preventing the overall connection from becoming ready until nw_framer_mark_ready(_:) is called.
